REFERENCE           21KJO008
LANG_ENGLISH        "I, I thought you were dead!"
LANG_CHINESE        "我，我以为你死了。"

REFERENCE           21JAO004
LANG_ENGLISH        "Dead?  No.  In pain, yes.  Desann and his thugs must've burned out a half-dozen interrogation Droids trying to get me to crack."
LANG_CHINESE        "死了？不。痛苦中，是的。迪桑和他的暴徒一定烧毁了六架审讯机器人，试图让我破解。"

REFERENCE           21KJO009
LANG_ENGLISH        "They wanted to know about the Valley of the Jedi, right?"
LANG_CHINESE        "他们想知道绝地谷的情况，对吧？"

