LANG_ENGLISH        "The Jedi Academy?"
LANG_CHINESE        "绝地学院？"

REFERENCE           21JAO006
LANG_ENGLISH        "Yeah. Desann seemed obsessed with it."
LANG_CHINESE        "是啊。迪桑似乎对此着迷。"

